ult=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Th.\">Th.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">4.27</biblScope></bibl>, etc.; <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">οἱ περιγενόμενοι</foreign> the <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">survivors</tr_>, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0016.tlg001.perseus-grc1:5:64\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Hdt.\">Hdt.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">5.64</biblScope></bibl>, etc.: c. gen. rei, <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">περιεγένετο τούτον τοῦ πάθεος</foreign> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">he survived, escaped from</tr_> this disaster, ib.<bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0016.tlg001.perseus-grc1:46\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">46</biblScope> </bibl> ; <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">τῆς δίκης π</foreign>. <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0059.tlg034.perseus-grc1:905a\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Pl.\">Pl.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Lg.\">Lg.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">905a</biblScope> </bibl> ; <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ἐκ τῶν μεγίστων π</foreign>. <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0003.tlg001.perseus-grc1:2:49\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Th.\">Th.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">2.49</biblScope></bibl>. </sense> <sense n=\"2\" id=\"n81191.3\" level=\"3\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> of things, <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">remain over and above</tr_>, opp. <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ἐπιλείπειν</foreign>, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0019.tlg011.perseus-grc1:554\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Ar.\">Ar.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Pl.\">Pl.</