te TEIform=\"date\">(iii B.C.)</date>, etc.; <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">τὰ περιγινόμενα</foreign> the <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">revenues</tr_>, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0074.tlg001:7:17:4\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\">Arr.</author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ An.\">An.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">7.17.4</biblScope></bibl>. </sense> <sense n=\"3\" id=\"n81191.4\" level=\"3\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> of things, <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">to be left over</tr_> : hence, <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">to be a result</tr_> or <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">consequence</tr_>, <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ἐκ τῶν μεγίστων κινδύνων καὶ πόλει καὶ ἰδιώτῃ μέγισται τιμαὶ π</foreign>. <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0003.tlg001.perseus-grc1:1:144\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Th.\">Th.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">1.144</biblScope> </bibl> ; <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">ἀμαχητὶ π. τινί τι</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0003.tlg001.perseus-grc1:4:73\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Id.\">Id.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">4.73</biblScope> </bibl> </cit> ; <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ἡ ἠθικὴ ἐξ ἔθους π</foreign>. <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0086.tlg010.perseus-grc1:1103a:17\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Arist.\">Arist.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ EN\">EN</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">1103a17</biblScope> </bibl> ; <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">τί αὐτῷ περιγέγονεν ἐκ τῆς φιλοσοφίας</foreign> ; <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0004.tlg001.perseus-grc1:2:68\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"