Lit:tlg0014.tlg063.perseus-grc1:3:36\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Id.\">Id.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Ep.\">Ep.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">3.36</biblScope> </bibl> ; <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ἀηδὴς δόξα τῇ πόλει παρὰ τοῖς πολλοῖς π</foreign>. <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0014.tlg062.perseus-grc1:23\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Id.\">Id.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Prooem.\">Prooem.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">23</biblScope> </bibl> ; <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">ἡ ἐκ τῆς πραγματικῆς ἱστορίας περιγινομένη ἐμπειρία</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0543.tlg001.perseus-grc1:1:35:9\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Plb.\">Plb.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">1.35.9</biblScope></bibl></cit>.</sense> </entryFree>"}]}